quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  64,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  64,1,Allah ki tasbeeh kar rahi hai har woh cheez jo asmano mein hai aur har woh cheez jo zameen mein hai isi ki badshahi hai aur isi ke liye tareef hai aur woh har cheez par Qadir hai
  64,2,"wohi hai jis ne tum ko peda kya, phir tum mein se koi kafir hai aur koi momin, aur Allah woh sab kuch dekh raha hai jo tum karte ho"
  64,3,"is ne zameen aur asmano ko barhaq peda kya hai, aur tumhari soorat banai aur barri umdah banai hai, aur isi ki taraf aakhir kaar tumhe palatna hai"
  64,4,"zameen aur asmano ki har cheez ka usay ilm hai jo kuch tum chupatay ho aur jo kuch tum zahir karte ho sab is ko maloom hai, aur woh dilon ka haal taq jaanta hai"
  64,5,kya tumhe unn logon ki koi khabar nahi pohanchi jinhon ne iss se pehlay kufar kya aur phir apni shamat aamaal ka maza chakh liya? aur agay unn ke liye aik dard naak azaab hai
  64,6,"iss injaam ke mustahiq woh is liye hue ke unn ke paas unn ke rasool khuli khuli daleelen aur nishanain le kar atay rahay, magar onhon ne kaha"" kya ensaan hamein hadaayat den ge ?"" is terhan unhon ne maan-ne se inkaar kar diya aur mun phair liya, tab Allah bhi un se be parwa ho gaya aur Allah to hai hi be niaz aur apni zaat mein aap Mahmood"
  64,7,"munkareen ne barray daaway se kaha hai ke woh marnay ke baad hargiz dobarah nah uthaye jayen ge un se kaho"" nahi, mere rab ki qasam tum zaroor uthaye jao ge, phir zaroor tumhe bataya jaye ga ke tum ne ( duniya mein ) kya kuch kya hai, aur aisa karna Allah ke liye bohat aasaan hai """
  64,8,"pas imaan lao Allah par, aur uss ke rasool par, aur uss roshni par jo hum ne nazil ki hai jo kuch tum karte ho Allah is se bakhabar hai"
  64,9,"( iss ka pata tumhe is roz chal jaye ga ) jab ijtima ke din woh tum sab ko akhatta kere ga woh din hoga aik dosray ke muqablay mein logon ki haar jeet ka jo Allah par imaan laya hai aur naik amal karta hai, Allah is ke gunah jhaad day ga aur usay aisijannaton mein daakhil kere ga jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi yeh log hamesha hamesha un mein rahen ge yeh barri kamyabi hai"
  64,10,aur jin logon ne kufar kya hai aur hamari ayaat ko jhtlaya hai woh dozakh ke bashinday hon ge jis mein woh hamesha rahen ge aur woh bad tareen thikana hai
  64,11,"koi museebat kabhi nahi aati magar Allah ke azan hi se aati hai jo shakhs Allah par imaan rakhta ho Allah is ke dil ko hadaayat bkhshta hai, aur Allah ko har cheez ka ilm hai"
  64,12,Allah ki itaat karo aur rasool ki taat karo lekin agar tum itaat se mun morty ho to hamaray rasool par saaf saaf haq pouncha dainay ke siwa koi zimma daari nahi hai
  64,13,"Allah woh hai jis ke siwa koi khuda nahi, lehaza imaan laane walon ko Allah hi par bhrosa rakhna chahiye"
  64,14,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, tumhari biwion aur tumhari aulaad mein se baaz tumahray dushman hain, un se hooshiyar raho aur agar tum Afoo o dar guzar se kaam lau aur maaf kar do to Allah ghafoor o Raheem hai"
  64,15,"tumahray maal aur tumhari aulaad to aik azmaish hain, aur Allah hi hai jis ke paas bara ajar hai"
  64,16,"lehaza jahan taq tumahray bas mein ho Allah se drtay raho, aur suno aur itaat karo, aur apne maal kharch karo, yeh tumahray hi liye behtar hai jo apne dil ki tangi se mehfooz reh gay bas wohi Falah panay walay hain"
  64,17,"agar tum Allah ko qarz husn do to woh tumhe kayi gina barha kar day ga aur tumahrayKasoroo-n se dar guzar farmaiye ga, Allah bara qadar daan aur Burdbar hai"
  64,18,"haazir aur gayab har cheez ko jaanta hai, zabardast aur Dana hai"
